          },
          "reviewBody": "It is the worst school ever. Bunch of thugs are running the school.\nKamal, the administrative officer behaves like a ruffian. It seems he was made the AO of the school as school couldn't find anyone else.\n\nThey cancelled my daughter's admission. When I asked for refund of my daughter's fee (Rs. 11000/-), they are coming with excused one after another. I am yet to get refund for the same. When I try to contact them, nobody picks up my call.\n\nPrincipal Ms. Shabana Arora is very arrogant. She is petrified of any parents asking her questions. AGM of the school Mr. Vivek Bharti tried to hide when asked about the refund. Kamal, the administrative officer has kept me waiting. He seems least bothered.\nI want parents to be very careful. School doesn't have good teacher and administration is worse. I have seen parents yelling at the counter every other day.\n\nI will escalate the issue very soon as it has been more than 3 months but still money hasn't been returned to me. Don't spoil your child's career by taking admission in this school.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
