            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Narayana e techno School, South City-2 is a good place for teaching. There is so many chance for growth. I am blessed because I am part of this knowledgeable, educational institutions. As a fresher or experienced teacher, you will learn many things here.\nOne thing you need to make sure is that you need to be well updated with the teaching pedagogy and have to be prepared to take up any kind of school related task or incharge for which training will be given at the school itself indirectly. Overall, it's a very fun place to work at with strict timings and a very caring and cooperative management and Principal.",
          "publisher": {
